French racing driver Romain Grosjean wins the 2012 Race of Champions with a 2–0 victory over Tom Kristensen in the final in Bangkok, Thailand. (Motorsport) (Autosport)The first legs of the 2012–13 UEFA Europa League quarter-finals are held in Europe. Fernando Torres scores twice and helps Chelsea to a 3–1 defeat of Rubin Kazan. (BBC)